data.description: $10,000 Credit to Buyers with a Full Price Offer of $314,900.This property features a new roof (2023) and new AC 92023). It is 3-bed, 2.5-bath townhome in Palm Springs. Spanning 1,540 sq ft across two stories with solid CBS construction. Private patio. Upstairs, the bedrooms include a master suite with an en-suite bathroom. Home in need of a little TLC come and make it your own. Enjoy community amenities like a pool and clubhouse. Perfectly located for convenience and tranquility.
